cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CL 

This paper is primarily focused on Information Retrieval (IR) and proposes a framework for Multi Period Information Retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR. The paper also makes use of statistical techniques and click models, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses user satisfaction and explores the performance of the proposed framework using search log data, which suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
